item.title: VENOM - By ELEOS
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
Wooooooow. Ok so, kind of reminds me of a more aggressive Glitch Mob, one of my faves. Put a label on this? I’m not sure. To let people kind of know what they are getting into I’d say Breakbeat. But this ain’t no Fatboy Slim lol.

I can’t get enough of stuff like this though, I know that. Liked and reposted!
